Package io.crums.sldg.packs

Class MorselPackBuilder

java.lang.Object
io.crums.sldg.packs.MorselPackBuilder
All Implemented Interfaces:
io.crums.io.Serial, EntryBag, MorselBag, PathBag, RowBag, TrailBag, io.crums.util.hash.Digest
Direct Known Subclasses:
DbMorselBuilder
public class MorselPackBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
implements MorselBag, io.crums.io.Serial
A mutable MorselBag whose serial form can be loaded as an immutable MorselPack. Unlike the other builders, this enforces the full business rules of the interface.
See Also:
MorselPack.load(ByteBuffer)

      public int addRows​(MorselPack mp) throws HashConflictException
      Adds all the rows in the given morsel pack. If this instance is empty, then all the rows in the pack are added. Otherwise, only linked information is added. I.e. if not empty, this method only allows adding detail to already known information.

      Throws:
